OL,3,CDoctors call for smacking to be banned
OL,4,Cin England and Northern Ireland
OL,6,FBans have already been introduced in
OL,7,FScotland and Wales in recent years,
OL,8,FITV News' Ian Woods reports
OL,10,Fshould be illegal in England and
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland, children's doctor
OL,12,Fhave said, claiming current laws are
OL,13,F"unjust" and "dangerously vague".
OL,15,FThe current law in England and
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland has created "grey
OL,17,Fareas" which mean there is sometimes a
OL,18,Fdefence to physical punishment, the
OL,19,FRoyal College of Paediatrics and Child
OL,20,FHealth (RCPCH) said.
