OL,3,CDoctors call for smacking to be banned
OL,4,Cin England and Northern Ireland
OL,6,F, including smacking, hitting,
OL,7,Fslapping and shaking, illegal in March
OL,8,F2022, while Scotland introduced a
OL,9,Fsimilar ban in November 2020.
OL,11,FThe RCPCH said amendments to the
OL,12,FChildren Act 2004 for England and the
OL,13,FLaw Reform Order 2006 for Northern
OL,14,FIreland "to remove the 'reasonable
OL,15,Fpunishment' defence from all UK law
OL,16,Fare long overdue".
