OL,6,FLabour MP Catherine McKinnell outlined
OL,7,Fthat her party want to 'end smacking
OL,8,Fof children' while pointing
OL,9,Flegislation in Scotland and Wales and
OL,10,Fhow similar law changes could be made
OL,11,Fin England
OL,13,FProfessor Andrew Rowland, a consultant
OL,14,Fpaediatrician and RCPCH officer for
OL,15,Fchild protection, said physical
OL,16,Fpunishment could also result in a
OL,17,Fchild having the learned belief that
OL,18,Fviolence was accepted and this could
OL,19,F"lead to further instances of violence
OL,20,Fand harm later in life".
